{"tid":2358403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「我道歉，但我冇錯，因為笑係人嘅自然反應，係忍唔住嘅。」","createTime":"2021-01-08T06:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T06:37:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98515b3c8131433b7209c1f926b235292020c6c7","tid":2358403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"「我道歉，但我冇錯，因為笑係人嘅自然反應，係忍唔住嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/J3JZ4UHJR5HABKOAPW37OQBCYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FJ3JZ4UHJR5HABKOAPW37OQBCYU%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=a8f12fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FJ3JZ4UHJR5HABKOAPW37OQBCYU%2F&h=7ed07b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/J3JZ4UHJR5HABKOAPW37OQBCYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n督察避答是片中人 官質問即認<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bC-Lf65OiEQ-igLlnEsMYgwKh64=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEWYWRJM5FA73CXACBUMUBWS4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbC-Lf65OiEQ-igLlnEsMYgwKh64%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEWYWRJM5FA73CXACBUMUBWS4Y.jpg&h=01a4af1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【阻差辦公案】【本報訊】前年10月31日多區集會，一名文員及網媒女記者分別被控襲警及阻差辦公，案件昨續審，一度稱女記者「令我追截慢咗一秒鐘嘅反應時間」的督察續作供。庭上播放當晚片段，督察多次以影像模糊「睇唔到」為由，避答是否身處片中。裁判官張天雁忍不住稱：「唔好不停話睇唔到，咁樣冇意思㗎。」督察最終表示：「法官閣下，我相信呢個係我本人。」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旁聽人士訕笑被請走<br />\n<br />\n庭上再播放當晚多部警車趕到現場片段，辯方問片段中有人從警車車頭位置下車，是否譚本人；譚健燊多次答影像模糊「睇唔到」。張官謂：「幫辦，你咁樣幫唔到法庭㗎。你可以話可能係我，唔好不停話睇唔到，咁樣冇意思㗎。」又謂「辯方大律師咁問你，係合理㗎&hellip;&hellip;你唔使勞氣，講證據就得㗎喇」，譚即確認該人是他。<br />\n<br />\n此時公眾席傳來笑聲，張官問：「邊個笑呀？」一名中年漢站立直言「係我笑」，並自行離座準備離開。張官謂：「你認錯道歉就得㗎喇。」男子謂：「我道歉，但我冇錯，因為笑係人嘅自然反應，係忍唔住嘅。」張官說：「咁你出去啦，你嘅忍耐能力咁低。」惟男子邊行邊說：「我出去，但我一啲都唔低。」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC668/20"},{"pid":"53ed45f28bb0018761e1ae5f02ce40be0e57add3","tid":2358403,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"咁好笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582b9dd30585f150e8e5044baca54bbc12da4cf3","tid":2358403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53ed45f28bb0018761e1ae5f02ce40be0e57add3","tid":2358403,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"咁好笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"你一啲都唔低"},{"pid":"e4d7eda0509e5a93b499d8242c78acae68ac741b","tid":2358403,"uid":216592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"笑9黑狗"},{"pid":"6e57bafc028d471a36f389f0dd665ab70671cc75","tid":2358403,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"狗官"}]}